.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
City: colone, hannover, rome, miami
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person traveling to miami is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person traveling to miami and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| City   | colone      | hannover  | miami  | rome |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
City: hamburg, edinburgh, prague, london
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person traveling to prague is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person eating lemon and the person traveling to edinburgh##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| City         | hamburg   | prague | london       | edinburgh    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

