.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, jet-ski, car
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person driving the train is between the fan of folk and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person who's sport is cricket and the dutch##2
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Transport           | jet-ski | train | motorbike  | car |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

