4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person eating apricot is the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the musician is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
8. the designer is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
9. the electrician is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
